> CONFIG_FB=y
> CONFIG_DUMMY_CONSOLE=y
> CONFIG_FB_VESA=y
> CONFIG_VIDEO_SELECT=y
> CONFIG_FB_ATY=y
You have two video cards? If not you have two fbdev drivers accessing the
same video card. Not good. If the ATI driver works for your video card use
that. Vesafb is very very slow and will give you the problems you desribe.
